*NORMAL TELEPORTER SCRIPT 1001 (called by ACTIVATE 1 and 2)
*(_P2_ is from, _P1_ is button part number/teleport destination: Random (3) or Home (2) (incubator room))

scrp 3 2 50202 1001

	lock

	inst

